Sumarizando as avaliaes

sumarise_exp02 <- data %>% 
    group_by(id, municipio, criterio, item, aproach, date) %>% 
    mutate(
           
           #verifica se a avaliao foi acertiva
           tp = (valid == TRUE 
           & valid == encontrado 
           #valida se no gabarito e na avaliao o item foi encontrado na mesma url 
           & (grepl(local_encontrado, pathSought) |
                  grepl(local_encontrado_2, pathSought))) | (valid == FALSE 
           & valid == encontrado),
           
           fn =  valid == FALSE 
           & encontrado == TRUE,
           
           fp = valid == TRUE 
           & encontrado == FALSE
          )

Quantificando mtricas

metricas_result_exp02 <- sumarise_exp02 %>% 
    #filter(!is.na(aproach )) %>% 
    group_by(municipio, aproach, date) %>% 
    summarise(
        total_itens = n(),
        tp_total = sum(tp), 
        fn_total = sum(fn),
        fp_total = sum(fp),
        
        #clculo das mtricas 
        recall = tp_total/(tp_total + fn_total),
        precision =  tp_total/(tp_total + fp_total),
        f1_score = (2*(recall*precision))/(recall+precision),
        
        #tempo das avaliaes
        median_duration_min = median(durationMin),
        median_duration = median(duration),
        max_duration = max(duration),
        max_durationMin = max(durationMin),
        median_num_access_node = median(contNodeNumberAccess),
        max_num_access_node = max(contNodeNumberAccess),
        all_access_node = sum(contNodeNumberAccess),
        combination = last(fornecedor),
        tipo_exp = last(tipo_exp)
    )


metricas_result_exp02 <- metricas_result_exp02 %>%
  filter(total_itens == 48 & recall > 0.46)

metricas_result_exp02 %>% 
    write_csv(here::here("data/resultados_sumarizado_exp.csv"))

Intervalo de Confiana da Mediana encontrada do F1 Score para cada Abordagem

#Calcula a media das posies escolhidas nas buscas.
set.seed(123)

recall_boot.exp02 <- function (d, i) {
    dt<-d[i,]
    return(c(
          median(dt$recall)
    ))
}

create_ic <- function(x) {
  x <- last(x)
  df.boot <- filter(metricas_result_exp02, aproach == x)
  
  bootstrap.aproach.exp02 <- boot(
          data = df.boot, 
          statistic = recall_boot.exp02, 
          R = 4000 )
  
  ci.exp2 = tidy(bootstrap.aproach.exp02, 
          conf.level = .95,
          conf.method = "bca",
          conf.int = TRUE)
  
  print(glimpse(ci.exp2))
  
  return(ci.exp2)
}


ics.aproach_exp02 <- metricas_result_exp02 %>%
  group_by(aproach) %>% 
   summarise(
     median_value = median(recall),
     ci = list(create_ic(aproach))
  ) %>% 
  unnest(ci)

#Calcula a media das posies escolhidas nas buscas.
set.seed(123)

precision_boot.exp02 <- function (d, i) {
    dt<-d[i,]
    return(c(
          median(dt$precision)
    ))
}

create_ic.exp02.precision <- function(x) {
  x <- last(x)
  df.boot <- filter(metricas_result_exp02, aproach == x)
  
  bootstrap.aproach.exp02.precision <- boot(
          data = df.boot, 
          statistic = precision_boot.exp02, 
          R = 4000 )
  
  ci.exp2.precision = tidy(bootstrap.aproach.exp02.precision, 
          conf.level = .95,
          conf.method = "bca",
          conf.int = TRUE)
  
  print(glimpse(ci.exp2.precision))
  
  return(ci.exp2.precision)
}

sumarise_exp02 %>% 
  group_by(municipio, criterio, aproach, date) %>% 
    summarise(
        total_itens = n(),
        tp_total = sum(tp), 
        fn_total = sum(fn),
        fp_total = sum(fp),
        
        #clculo das mtricas 
        recall = tp_total/(tp_total + fn_total),
        precision =  tp_total/(tp_total + fp_total),
        f1_score = (2*(recall*precision))/(recall+precision),
        
        #tempo das avaliaes
        median_duration_min = median(durationMin),
        median_duration = median(duration),
        max_duration = max(duration),
        max_durationMin = max(durationMin),
        median_num_access_node = median(contNodeNumberAccess),
        max_num_access_node = max(contNodeNumberAccess),
        all_access_node = sum(contNodeNumberAccess),
        combination = last(fornecedor),
        tipo_exp = last(tipo_exp)
    ) %>%
  filter(total_itens == tp_total) %>%
  group_by(criterio) %>%
  summarise(n = n()) %>%
  arrange(desc(n))
